MERN Blog App

Features;

-User authentication with JWT

-Register and Login

-Create, Read, Update, Delete posts

-View all posts on the homepage

-View single post details

-Protected routes for creating and editing posts

-Delete posts with confirmation

-Toast notifications for success/error messages

-Responsive and interactive UI with Tailwind + shadcn

Backend structure
backend/
├── controllers/
│   ├── authController.js
│   └── postController.js
├── middleware/
│   └── authMiddleware.js
├── models/
│   ├── userModel.js
│   └── postModel.js
├── routes/
│   ├── authRoutes.js
│   └── postRoutes.js
├── server.js
└── .env
Frontend structure
frontend/
├── index.html
├── package.json
├── vite.config.js
└── src/
    ├── main.jsx
    ├── App.jsx
    ├── api/axios.js
    ├── components/
    │   ├── Navbar.jsx
    │   └── PostCard.jsx
    ├── context/
    │   ├── AuthContext.jsx
    │   └── ToastContext.jsx
    ├── lib/utils.js
    ├── pages/
    │   ├── Home.jsx
    │   ├── Login.jsx
    │   ├── Register.jsx
    │   ├── CreatePost.jsx
    │   ├── EditPost.jsx
    │   └── ViewPost.jsx
    └── styles/index.css

Run:npm run dev (both on front end and backend to get the up and running)
